bicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1013525, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "Middle portion is called Dakkatul Meraj (Seat of the Ascension to the Heavens). We must perform Aamal in the middle part of Masjid. May be the Prophet (s) had recited prayers at this same place on the Meraj night. Recite 2 rakat namaz. In the 1st rakat after <Surah Fateha> recite <Surah Ikhlaas> and in the 2nd rakat after <Surah Fateha> recite <Surah Kaaferoon>. After Tasbeeh-e-Zahra (s) recite…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Masjid ke wusta (beech ke) hisse ko Dakkatul Meraj (Meraj ki taraf jaane ka maqaam) bi kaha jaata hai. Is maqaam par hamein amal karna chahiye. Mumqeen hai keh Rasool-e-Khuda (s) Meraj pe jaate waqt is jagah par namaz padhi ho. Yahan par 2 rakat namaz adaa kare. 1st rakat mein <Surah Fateha> ke baad <Surah Ikhlaas> padhe aur 2nd rakat mein <Surah Fateha> ke baad <Surah Kaaferoon> padhe. Tasbeeh-e-Zahra (s) ke baad yeh padhe…", "UrduDescription": "مؤلف کہتے ہیں: اس مقام کو دکۃ المعراج بھی کہا جاتا ہے اس کی وجہ شاید یہ ہو کہ شب ِمعراج حضرت رسول اﷲؐاﷲتعالیٰ سے اجازت لے کریہیں اترے ہوں اور نماز بجالائے ہوں، یہ درمیانِ مسجدہیں یہاں پر ۲ رکعت نماز بجا لائے کہ اس کی پہلی رکعت میں <سورۂ فاتحہ> کے بعد <سورۂ اخلاص> اور دوسری رکعت میں <سورۂ فاتحہ> کے بعد <سورۂ کافرون> کی تلاوت کرے،نمازکے بعد تسبیح فاطمہ زہراء ؑ اور پھر یہ دعا پڑھے۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 1, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "In the Name of Allah, the most Gracious, the most Merciful.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "(Shuru karta hu) Allah ke naam se Jo bada maher-baan nehaayat rahem karne waala hai.", "Urdu": "اللہ کے نام سے (شروع کرتا ہوں) جو بڑا مہربا ن نہایت رحم کرنے والا ہے۔", "RArabic": "BISMILLAAHIR RAHMAANIR RAHEEM", "ArabicText1": "بِسْمِ اللہِ الرَّحْمٰنِ الرَّحِیْمِ", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1013526, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O Allah, You are the Peace. You are the source of peace. To You does peace belong. Your abode is the abode of peace. Your abode is the abode of peace. O Allah, I have offered this prayer, seeking Your mercy, pleasure, forgiveness, and as sign of my esteeming Your mosque. O Allah, (please) send blessings upon Muhammad and the Household of Muhammad, raise my prayer to the most elevated place, and accept it from me, O most merciful of all those who show mercy.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay Ma’bood! Tu salaamati waala hai aur salaamati Tujh se milti hai aur salaamati Teri taraf palat-ti hai, Teri baargah salaamati ka markaz hai. Hamare Parwardigaar hamein salaamati ke saath zindah rakh. Ay Ma’bood! Be-shak mai ne namaz adaa ki yeh keh mai Teri rehmat chahta hu, Teri khushnoodi aur Tujh se maafi talab karta hu, neez Teri masjid ki taazeem ke liye yeh namaz padhi hai. Ay Ma’bood! Tu Muhammad (s.a.w.a) wa Aale Muhammad (a.s) par rehmat farma, unko maqaame illiyyin par buland kar aur meri namaz qabool farma, ay sab se ziyadah rahem waale.", "Urdu": "اے معبود! تو سلامتی والا ہے اور سلامتی تجھ سے ملتی ہے اور سلامتی تیری طرف پلٹتی ہے تیری بارگاہ سلامتی کا مرکز ہے ہمارے پروردگار ہمیں سلامتی کے ساتھ زندہ رکھ اے معبود!بے شک میں نے نماز ادا کی یہ کہ میں تیری رحمت کا حصول چاہتا ہوں تیری خوشنودی اور تجھ سے معافی طلب کرتا ہوں نیز تیری مسجد کی تعظیم کے لئے یہ نماز پڑھی ہے اے معبود! تو محمدؐ و آل محمدؑ پر رحمت فرما ان کو مقام ِعلیین پر بلند کر اور میری نماز قبول فرما اے سب سے زیادہ رحم کرنے والے۔", "RArabic": "ALLAAHUMMA ANTAS SALAAMO WA MINKAS SALAAMO WA ILAIKA YA-O’ODUS SALAAMO WA DAAROKA DAARUS SALAAME HAYYENAA RABBANAA MINKA BIS-SALAAME ALLAAHUMMA INNEE SALLAYTO HAAZEHIS SALAATAB TEGHAAA-A RAHMATEKA WA RIZWAANEKA WA MAGHFERATEKA WA TA’ZEEMAL LE-MASJEDEKA ALLAAHUMMA FA-SALLE A’LAA MOHAMMADIWN WA AALE MOHAMMADIWN WAR-FA’HAA FEE I’LLIYYEENA WA TAQABBALHAA MINNEE YAA ARHAMAR RAAHEMEEN.", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ اَنْتَ السَّلَامُ وَمِنْكَ السَّلَامُ وَاِلَیْكَ یَعُوْدُ السَّلَامُ وَدَارُكَ دَارُ السَّلَامِ حَیِّنَا رَبَّنَا مِنْكَ بِالسَّلَامِ۔ اَللّٰهُمَّ اِنِّیْ صَلَّیْتُ هٰذِهِ الصَّلٰوۃَ ابْتِغَآءَ رَحْمَتِكَ وَرِضْوَانِكَ وَمَغْفِرَتِكَ وَتَعْظِیْمًا لِّمَسْجِدِكَ۔ اَللّٰهُمَّ فَصَلِّ عَلٰی مُحَمَّدٍ وَّاٰلِ مُحَمَّدٍ وَّارْفَعْهَا فِیْ عِلِّیِّیْنَ وَتَقَبَّلْهَا مِنِّیْ یَآ اَرْحَمَ الرَّاحِمِیْنَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "A